---
title: Herbed Chicken & Roast Veggie Toss with Yoghurt & Chargrilled Capsicum Relish
description: Smell the sweet scent of bliss when you sit down to eat this bowl of nutritious goodness. The fresh veggies, roasted to sweet perfection create a bed for the tender chicken breast strips to rest on. A delicious capsicum relish and yoghurt combo will have you feeling like you’re on a sunny holiday!
This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.
